= toys-python
Al Idian <al.idian@acm.org>
:description: A collection of (very) small programs in Python

`toys` is a collection of (very) small programs, each meant to show just one or two competencies.

Setup:

[source,bash]
----
# Start a toolbox container
docker run --name toys-python -it -v "$(pwd)":/home/idianal/toys-python idianal/toolbox

# Inside the container, install required packages
apt update
apt install -y python3
----
